ygData.messageBody:
I currently have a gnome necromancer on erolissi marr and I have journeyed to
greater faydark to take on orcs and hunt in cb to get money for those
expensive spells at 8th level. The guards hate me of course and by killing
orcs already Ive gotten my faction up with kelethin guards(stormguard?) so
that only some of them kos me(which is kind of odd). I was just wondering if
killing orcs also raises your faction with guards of felwithe or if it doesnt
what does.

~Daemon
